a \ud83c\udf5c\r\nI usually enjoy listening to music \ud83c\udfa7\uff0c Write music \ud83c\udfb8\uff0c play a game \ud83c\udfae\uff0c Type code \u2328\ufe0f\r\nShare some code, research, and daily life \ud83d\ude04\r\n\r\n### Hallo\r\nIch bin Alan Hu, ein gutaussehender Kerl, der am Himmel auff\u00e4llt! \ud83d\ude1c\r\nIch komme aus Nanchang, Jiangxi, China \ud83c\udf5c\r\nIch h\u00f6re normalerweise gerne Musik. \ud83c\udfa7\uff0c Musik schreiben \ud83c\udfb8\uff0c ein Spiel spielen \ud83c\udfae\uff0c Typencode \u2328\ufe0f\r\nTeilen Sie Code und Alltag \ud83d\ude04\r\n\r\n### \u3053\u3093\u306b\u3061\u306f\r\n\u79c1\u306fAlan Hu\u3067\u3059\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1733117256, "style": "", "script": "<script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/GmeekTOC.js'></script><script src='https://blog.meekdai.com/Gmeek/plugins/lightbox.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://img0.baidu.com/it/u=2381411310,900662946&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=800&h=800", "createdDate": "2024-12-02", "dateLabelColor": "#bc4c00"}}, "labelColorDict": {"about": "#C2E0C6", "bug": "#d73a4a", "documentation": "#0075ca", "duplicate": "#cfd3d7", "enhancement": "#a2eeef", "good first issue": "#7057ff", "help wanted": "#008672", "invalid": "#e4e669", "question": "#d876e3", "wontfix": "#ffffff"}, "displayTitle": "Alan Hu", "faviconUrl": "https://img0.baidu.com/it/u=2381411310,900662946&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=800&h=800", "ogImage": "https://img0.baidu.com/it/u=2381411310,900662946&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=800&h=800", "primerCSS": "<link href='https://mirrors.sustech.edu.cn/cdnjs/ajax/libs/Primer/21.0.7/primer.css' rel='stylesheet' />", "homeUrl": "https://hu-aniu.github.io", "prevUrl": "disabled", "nextUrl": "disabled"}